  "detailed_description": "<strong>STORY</strong><br><br>Jim's old house was unoccupied for the summer, so the three friends decided to move in together. A wonderful vacation was expecting, but something horrible happened. <br><br>Escape from the manor house and explore the garden with statuettes to get and easter eggs to find. Ah, there's a small detail, you won't be alone...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595370/extras/56b3a6b826a521ffcdc5f3368a75d991.poster.avif?t=1696177341\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595370/extras/56b3a6b826a521ffcdc5f3368a75d991.webm?t=1696177341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595370/extras/56b3a6b826a521ffcdc5f3368a75d991.mp4?t=1696177341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>ENVIROMENT</strong><br><br>Explore the garden engulfed in darkness without getting caught by the beast. The manor is your safe place, full of tools and a music box that is best not to be near for too long...<br><br><br><br><strong>CHARACTER</strong><br><br>You can't wait to spend some time with your best friends Jim and Jhon.<br><br>Run to the gardener who can't wait to greet you.<br><br>Can you figure out who Professor Terry is?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595370/extras/eea6517ce5c7cecf8fcd67150eaf721f.poster.avif?t=1696177341\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595370/extras/eea6517ce5c7cecf8fcd67150eaf721f.webm?t=1696177341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595370/extras/eea6517ce5c7cecf8fcd67150eaf721f.mp4?t=1696177341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>FIND THE  STATUETTES</strong><br><br>There are seven statuettes to find. Will you be able to find them all?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595370/extras/784f84d2b62f071d4978585ea49a289e.poster.avif?t=1696177341\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595370/extras/784f84d2b62f071d4978585ea49a289e.webm?t=1696177341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595370/extras/784f84d2b62f071d4978585ea49a289e.mp4?t=1696177341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
